<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>标题</strong>：有所思</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/think-cyan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4886286); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4886286&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663837" alt="Think cyan" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4886286)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/think-cyan" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4886286); return false;">Think cyan</a></span>，进入<a href="/think-cyan-s-personnel-file">念青的人事档案</a>查看该作者的更多作品。</p>
<p><strong>备注</strong>：本文世界观基于<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/dummy-html">三千无光之年</a>，挑战成就“一衣带水”<br />
图源：<a href="https://i.loli.net/2020/03/20/z5tAkGDvgm1hHQB.jpg">https://i.loli.net/2020/03/20/z5tAkGDvgm1hHQB.jpg</a><br />
由<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku393" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2996561); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2996561&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663837" alt="miku393" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2996561)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku393" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2996561); return false;">miku393</a></span>上传于<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/gallery">http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/gallery</a></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div class="creditBottomRate" style="position:relative;height:30px;">
<div style="text-align: center; top: 0px;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+26</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
